underlying_goal: To create a complete, publication-ready technical report and a deployable web application from a detailed plan.
friction_detail: Initial permission issues and a Python dependency failure required workarounds. The user had to make several corrections to the final PDF's author information and headers.

brief_summary: Following a detailed plan, Claude generated a complete technical report in LaTeX, including data analysis and figure creation.
